aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Plug and Play 
Easy to use, just plug it into your USB interface, now start your entertainment and work with usb thumb drive. The thumb drive has the compatibility of FAT32, exFAT and NTFS format. 
Retractable Design 
Retractable design provides efficient protection to the USB port, the capless design can avoid losing of cap. ABS plastic body make it solid and durable. 
Safely Take Your Data Anywhere 
Fashionable black body design with a lanyard hole that can easily be attached to your key chain or lanyard. 
Aiibe 128 GB Flash Drive Single USB 128GB Thumb Drive 128G USB Flash Drive 128 GB USB 2.0 Memory Stick, Green 
The flash drive comes with 128GB of storage, which should accommodate up to 12800 songs. It has a black plastic finish and a green switch-like mechanism on the side that will allow you to extend the USB connector or retract it. The feature means you can keep your USB connector safe when it’s not in use and makes the flash drive a little bit smaller and therefore easier to pop in your pocket. 
Specifications: 
Capacity: 128GB 
Chip: Grade A, original brand flash memory chip. 
Interface: USB 2.0 
Speed: Write Speed: 8MB/S-12 MB/S; Read Speed: 20MB/S-25MB/S. 
Operating Temperatures: 0ºC to 60ºC 
Storage Temperatures: -20ºC to 85ºC 
Compatibility: All brands of Desktop PC, Laptop and others consumer electronic device with USB interface, etc. 
Operating System: Supports almost all operating system including Windows 2000/7/8/8.1/10/Vista/XP/2000/ME, Linux and MacOs 10.3 and above. 
Widely Used: 
Use the thumb drive to promote your brand as this drive is blank without any logo.
You can store Digital Brochures, Instruction Manuals, Software in the jump drive and provide it to the customers with your products or services.
You can load a promotional video in the pen drive and provide it to your customers in an event.
Print the flash drive with your company’s logo and provide company’s overview, data, etc. to the new employees.
Can be used in schools, colleges, universities and other professional institutes to provide study material to their students.
Notes: 
(1) 128GB USB flash drive 2.0: the actual usable capacity is about 115GB as some of the capacity is used for format of other function. 
(2) USB drive transfer speed performance may vary by capacities depending on host device, file attributes and other factors.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
SanDisk Ultra Dual Drive USB Type-C 
Easily free up space on your smartphone (1) or quickly transfer files between devices at USB 3.1 high speeds of up to 150MB/s (2). With a reversible USB Type-C connector and a traditional USB connector, the SanDisk Ultra Dual Drive USB Type-C lets you quickly and easily transfer files between smartphones, tablets and computers. The SanDisk Memory Zone app for Android (available on Google Play) (3) helps you manage your device’s memory and your content. 
SanDisk products are constructed to the highest standards and rigorously tested. You can be confident in the outstanding quality, performance and reliability of every SanDisk product. 
What's in the Box? 
SanDisk Ultra Dual Drive USB Type-C
At a Glance: 
Easy transfer between smartphones, tablets (1) and PC and Mac computers 
Free up space on your Android smartphone (1) 
USB Type-C connector and a traditional USB connector 
High-speed USB 3.1 performance of up to 150MB/s (2) 
SanDisk Memory Zone file management app for easy back up (3) 
Compatible with USB Type-C Devices 
The SanDisk Ultra Dual Drive USB Type-C Flash Drive is designed specifically for next-generation devices with the new USB Type-C port. The reversible connector has a symmetric design that is always right-side up, making it easy to plug in. 
High-Speed USB 3.1 Performance 
With high-speed USB 3.1 performance of up to 150MB/s (2), the Ultra Dual Drive lets you quickly and easily transfer photos, videos, songs, and other files between devices. 
Dual USB Type-C and Type-A Connectors 
With dual USB connectors, the Ultra Dual Drive is compatible with both the new USB Type-C ports and the traditional USB Type-A ports. Use it to free up space on your smartphone or tablet (1) or transfer files between multiple devices. 
SanDisk Memory Zone App for Easy File Management 
Available from the Google Play store, the SanDisk Memory Zone app (3) lets you view, access, and back up all the files from your phone's memory in one location. It can also automatically move files from your device to your drive to free up space. 
Compatible with USB 3.0 and 2.0 Ports 
The SanDisk Ultra Dual Drive USB Type-C Flash Drive is backward-compatible with USB 2.0, so you can plug it into any USB 3.0 or 2.0 port. 
Choose the Amount of Storage You Need 
The amount of capacity you need depends on the types and number of files you have and their size. The chart above gives you an idea of how many photos, videos, and music and other files you can store for each capacity.

Wireless connectivity makes everything easier!

1. Station Mode 
Upgrade your Desktop PC to connect to the Wi-Fi network without the limitation of wired cable.
Help your Laptop get a more stable connection and faster wifi network speed.

Create a WiFi hotspot for other wireless devices to connect to.

Secure WiFi Connection

Benefits of Using the Mini Wireless WiFi Adapter: 
No more worrying about cluttered Ethernet cables. A tidy desk or space will put you in a better mood.
Not limited by the length of the Ethernet cable, you can freely choose where to place your computer.
Mini Design, Easy to Carry and Use 
This wifi dongle adapter is very small and will not affect your use of other USB ports on your Laptop.
Compared to traditional wireless network card or adapter with antennas, it is more convenient to use on the go. It weighs only 9g, so there is no burden to carry.

1.Please check if the nearby router's WiFi function works properly when connected directly to the cellphone.

To avoid any delay in reconnecting to the router after inactivity, we suggest you to turn off the power-saving mode of PC, otherwise it will take about 5-10 seconds to reconnect to the router when the PC awakes after inactivity.

items.text: 1.Please check if the nearby router's WiFi function works properly when connected directly to the cellphone.  2.Try adjusting the distance between the adapter and the router to avoid obstacles such thick walls and metal.

items.name: I have successfully got a connection, but the internet speed is slow. Is there a way to improve it?
items.text: 1.Connect the WiFi adapter to the USB3.0 port of your PC, that is blue color or marked USB3.0.  2.If you are originally connected to a 2.4GHz network, please change the wireless router from 2.4GHz to 5GHz and try again.

items.name: The internet is disconnected when the computer wakes up after a period of inactivity?
items.text: To avoid any delay in reconnecting to the router after inactivity, we suggest you to turn off the power-saving mode of PC, otherwise it will take about 5-10 seconds to reconnect to the router when the PC awakes after inactivity.

items.name: Connected, But no 5G WiFi signal, How to set?
items.text: 1.Ensure that your router supports 5G.  2.Turn off the "Combine 2.4GHz and 5GHz WiFi network" setting in the wifi and then you can manually choose 2.4G or 5G.

Rigorous and Meticulous Design Details: 
Swivel Series 
The 360° rotating metal clip protects the USB interface from damage when not in use. Unlike plastic ones, this metal-capped thumb drive is more elegant and durable, and will not crack even after using for a long time. 
Plug & Play 
No need to install any software, just plug into the USB port of computer or other devices and use it! 
Portability 
The small ring is designed for key chains or lanyards. You can take your digital world anywhere, without worrying about losing the pen drive. 
Most Cost-effective Wholesale 
The more quantity you buy from us, the more affordable each USB stick will be. And we are very confident in the quality of our products. Many repeat customers purchase hundreds and thousands of USB drives from us every year. 
Product Feature: 
Casing Materials 	Aluminum and Plastic 	
Colors 	Multi Color Case + Silver Cap 	
Each Size 	57*19*11 mm(Folded) 	
Weight 	9 Grams/ Unit 	
Chip 	Grade A, Original Brand Flash Memory Chip 	
Speed 	Write Speed:6MB/S-8MB/S; Read Speed:15MB/S-18MB/S 	
Interface 	USB 2.0, Backwards Compatible to USB 1.1 	
Durability 	50,000 Times Read & Write 	
Operating System 	Windows XP/ 2000/ Vista/ 7/ 8/ 8.1/ 10/ NT Linus/ MAC OS 10.4 and Higher 	
Operating Temperatures 	32º F to 140º F (0º C to 60º C) 	
Storage Temperatures 	-4º F to 185º F (-20º C to 85º C) 	
4~32GB Default Format 	FAT32 ( Could be Formatted to FAT | exFAT | NTFS ) 	
128MB~2GB Default Format 	FAT 	
Real Capacity - No Fake Capacity Expansion 
The actual available capacity of the small usb flash memory drive is a little smaller than we listed, because of different calculations between the computer and manufacturer: 
Computer: 1MB=1024KB, 1GB=1024MB
Manufacturer: 1MB=1000KB, 1GB=1000MB
And a reserved space is drawn for the stability of the main control and the life of the flash memory. 
Actual capacity of: 
128MB: approximately 106-121MB.
256MB: approximately 240-250MB.
512MB: approximately 480-505MB.
1GB: approximately 950-970MB.
2GB: approximately 1.7-1.8GB.
4GB: approximately 3.5-3.7GB.
8GB: approximately 7.3-7.6GB.
16GB: approximately 14GB-15GB.
32GB: approximately 29GB-30GB.
64GB: approximately 58GB-60GB.
Tips: 
Do not pull out the USB flash drive while reading or saving data. The interruption may damage the data or damage the USB flash drive.
Don't operate the files in the USB flash directly. It would better first copy the files to computer to operate and then copy back to USB flash after operation.
To extend USB flash's life span, it would better to plug the USB flash drive down after operation asap.
Before removing the USB, please delete the symbol on the bottom right of the PC screen to avoid missing files in the dish.
Please do not format the USB frequently for it may damage the USB flash.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
ONLY SUITABLE FOR PRECISION REPAIR 
Previous page
Next page
The Fanttik E1 Max Precision Electric Screwdriver is a must-have tool for the DIY Enthusiast! Simple operation and compact storage system allow you to complete tasks more efficiently. 9 types of 50 bits combined with pry bars and tweezers are suitable for a variety of electronic repair projects! 
TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS 
Previous page
Next page
Circular LED Light 
The LED light will be activated when working, even in a dim working environment, you can clearly see whether the screws are aligned with the holes. 
Universal USB-C Port 
The USB-C charging port is common in popular electronic products and is compatible with most current chargers, making charging more convenient. 
How can I see how much battery power left? 
When the battery level is below 20% in use, the indicator will rapidly blink red for 5 seconds. 
When charging, the indicator will slowly blink red. 
When fully charging, the indicator will become solid white. 
What's the real torque of E1 Max? 
E1 Max has 2 torque settings, the low torque 0.05 N.m and the high torque 0.2 N.m can be adjusted through the rotary knob. 
Twist to the LOCK SIGN, the gearbox will be locked, manual mode can be used at this time, max manual torque is 3 N.m 
Relationship between the preset torque and speed. 
Switching the torque does not affect the speed, but only affects the torque of the screwdriver on the screw. 
E1 Max unloaded speed is constant at 200 rpm. The sound produced by rotation has nothing to do with the torque. 
What are the applicable scenarios? 
E1 Max is only suitable for the repair of Precision Instruments, such as phones, drones, laptops, steamdeck, watch, etc. Not suitable for PC Assembly. 
If you need something with larger torque, opt for our S1 Pro Cordless Electric Screwdriver.

What shipping methods do you use ? How long does it take to deliver? 
Fulfillment of our standard USB Drives is handled exclusively by Amazon. 
Fulfillment for our Custom USB Drives is handled by Enfain Direct. It will take 7-12 business days to deliver by International Express. 
Can you imprint our logo on the USB? MOQ? 
Yes, we could print or engrave your logo on 2-side of the USB drives. 
Customized Swivel Flash Drives MOQ : 10 PCS/SKU | Credit Card Flash Drive MOQ: 50 PCS/ SKU 
How should I send logo/ artworks to you when I place a customized USB order? 
There are three ways to send us logo/ artworks. 
Opt.1: Upload your image or Add text by clicking " Customize Now" in order page. 
Opt. 2: Send your designs via Amazon buyer-seller message-Attach File. 
Opt. 3: Send your designs via email. 
Is there any discount if we order large quantity ? 
Yes, we provide discounts based on Quantity. If you are a business buyer registered on Amazon, you will be getting the discounts automatically. 
The actual storage is approximately 93% of the label storage. Why? 
The key is the different definitions of a GB from a Operating System and a Disk Drive Manufacturer. 
1. Operating Systems define a GB as 2^30 (1,073,741,824 bytes) 
2. Disk Drive Manufacturers define a GB as 10^9 (one billion bytes).

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
LESOGE MFI certi-fied USB flash drives give you a unique experience. 
It's the perfect storage solution on the go！ 
With exceptional storage capacity, it allows you to backup and share all valuable files, photos, videos, and more. The 3-in-1 photo stick for iPhone offers a stylish and sophisticated design that is compatible for features. 
It easily connects to your keychain and backpack, ensuring your personal documents are never forgotten. 
Improve personal privacy protection 
The iphone usb storage flash drive features password protection to ensure data security. You can set a password to protect the specific files. 
Dual chip design 
Intelligent upgrade chips ensure higher efficiency, security, and stability for data transmission. With the LESOGE iphone flash drive 512gb, you'll enjoy a better storage experience. 
Better compatibility 
The flash drive for iphone is compatible for ios7.1.2 and above ios devices/OTG Android phones/computers and other USB interface devices. Extensive compatibility allows you to freely transfer data between different devices. 
Store photos anytime, anywhere: All photos and videos can be directly saved to the usb storage flash drive, eliminating concerns of insufficient phone memory. 
About usb flash drive: 
1. For iPhone/iPad users, you need to download an APP "LESOGE", which you can search for from the APP store. 
(When the phone does not recognize the iphone picture storage stick, please uninstall the "LESOGE” APP, then restart the phone and manually download the LESOGE APP from the APP Store) 
2. For Android / PC users, our photo stick is plug and play. (Tips: only support Android phones with OTG function) 
3. If you used iCloud before, you need to download files to your iPhone/iPad and then copy them to the iphone external storage. 
Kindly note： 
1. You cannot transfer or view media files downloaded from iTunes or other third-party applications. Because these files are protected by digital rights management. 
2. After using the photo stick, please make sure to turn off the APP related to the iphone flash drive, and then unplug the lightning flash drive gently, so that the files in the thumb drive will not be damaged. 
3. The recommended format is "exFAT". If the jump drive cannot transfer files, you can convert the USB flash drive to "exFAT" format through the computer. (Please save the file before formatting to avoid data loss)

Easy to Use: This 1GB thumb drive is plug-and-play and can be used with any computer that has a USB 2.0 port. It is compatible with most operating systems, including Windows 7/8/10/11, Vista, XP, Unix, 2000, ME, NT, Mac, and Linux
High-Speed Data Transfer: These 1GB flash drives feature a USB 2.0 interface, providing fast and reliable data transfer speeds. Quickly transfer files between devices and share your data with ease

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Product description 
CHIP : Grade A, original brand flash memory chip 
Interface Type:USB 2.0 (backwards compatible to USB 1.1) 
Operating temperatures:32º F to 140º F (0º C to 60º C) 
Storage temperatures：-4º F to 185º F (-20º C to 85º C) 
Versatile File Compatibility 
It supports a wide range of digital file formats, including music, photos, movies, designs, programs, etc. Compatible formats include MP3, MP4, RMVB, EXCEL, WORD, PDF, etc. 
Compatibility and Storage Space 
1-2GB Default format is FAT16, 4GB-32GB Default format is FAT32. 64GB-128GB Default format is EXFAT. The thumb drive has the compatibility of FAT32, exFAT and NTFS format. If tranfer single file larger than 4GB, please format it to NTFS format! 
Capacity: Each flash drive has a reserved memory for formatting and other functions. The actual capacity is around 85%-90% of the nominal capacity. For example, the actual capacity of a 32GB flash drive is 27.2GB or 27.2GB above. 
360° Rotation Design 
With a rotating design, the USB metal clip can swivel 360° around the ABS plastic body, protect the USB interface from damage. 
Multi-device Support 
With our USB flash drives, you can store and share data between different devices like TVs, laptops, desktop computers, and car audio systems. 
Portable design 
The end of the Thumb Drive has a loop that can easily be attached to your key chain or lanyard, we have provided the free lanyard.
